<%= render 'layouts/header' %>

<div class="wind">
    <div class="row" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;">
    	<div class="col-md-12 text-center">
    		<h1 style="text-transform: uppercase;font-family:oseb;color:black;">BUILD YOUR ULTIMATE WINE EXPERIENCE HERE</h1>
    		<h2 style="font-style: italic;color:#b03441;margin-bottom: 60px;font-family:osbi;">Never wing it in wine country again</h2>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center content">
				<div class="" style="opacity:1;">
         		<h3 style="color:white;font-family:osb;">Where do you want to find tasting rooms?</h3>
	  				<form method="get" action="/wineries/" role="search" style="border: 0px none;">
              <!-- <input name="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>" type="hidden"> -->
              <div class="input-group input-group-lg search">
  						<span class="input-group-addon" id="sizing-addon1" style="padding-top: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 6px !important;">
  							<img src="<%= asset_path('map-pin.png') %>"/>
  						</span>
  					  <input type="text" class="form-control search-box" placeholder="Who, what, where, wine…" aria-describedby="sizing-addon1" style="font-family:osi" name="search_data">
  						<span class="input-group-btn" id="sizing-addon2">
  							<button type="submit" class="btn btn-default " style="background-color:#b03441;color:#ffffff;border: none;">GO</button>
  						</span>
  					</div>
          </form>
	        <div class="search">
  					<a href="#" class="text-right" style="text-transform: uppercase;float:right;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline; padding-top:10px;font-family:osb;">View All Wineries</a>
	    		</div>
	      </div>
    	</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid" style="background:#eeeded; padding-bottom:50px;">
  <div class="col-md-12 text-center" style="margin: 70px 0 70px 0">
    <h1 style="text-transform: uppercase;font-family:oseb;color:black;">How it works</h1>
  </div>
  <div style="margin:auto;width:87%">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12" style="text-align:center;">
        <img style="height: 60px;" src="<%= asset_path('plan.png') %>"/>
        <h2 style="font-family:osb;color: #B03441;">CREATE</h2>
        <h2 style="font-family:osl;color: #B03441;margin-top:10px;">your ultimate wine experience</h2>
        <p class="sizexs" style="text-align:justify;padding:0 30px;font-family:osr;">Want to find the next cult Napa Cabernet? Celebrate a sunny day in Sonoma? Meander the mountains in Mendoza? Have a romantic rendezvous in the Rhone? Whether you’re planning in advance or flying by the seat of your skinny jeans, you can create your ultimate wine experience, keep it close at hand, and watch it unfold before your eyes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12" style="text-align:center;">
        <img style="height: 60px;" src="<%= asset_path('bg.png') %>"/>
        <h2 style="font-family:osb;color: #B03441;">ENJOY</h2>
        <h2 style="font-family:osl;color: #B03441;margin-top:10px;">the grapes of your labor</h2>
        <p class="sizexs" style="text-align:justify;padding:0 30px;font-family:osr;">You’ve made your list and checked it twice… now it’s time to fill your glass and let your hair down. The targets are in sight. Get ready to enjoy your day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12" style="text-align:center;">
        <img style="height: 60px;" src="<%= asset_path('discover.png') %>"/>
        <h2 style="font-family:osb;color: #B03441;">REMEMBER</h2>
        <h2 style="font-family:osl;color: #B03441;margin-top:10px;">the time</h2>
        <p  class="sizexs" style="text-align:justify;padding:0 30px;font-family:osr;">Yeah you do…you’re oeno-mad! And now you’ve got your places, faces, and favorites all saved in one place. Want to know where your friends have been and what they thought? How about other oenomads in the community or the wine pros? Yeah, you’ve got that too. Sharing is caring! So be sure to share your experiences with others.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid" style="margin-bottom:50px;">
  <div class="col-md-12 text-center" style="margin: 50px 0 30px 0">
    <h1 style="text-transform: uppercase;font-family:oseb;color:black;">Explore</h1>
    <h3 style="font-style: italic;color:#b03441;font-family:osb;">Get inspired</h3>
  </div>
  <div style="margin:auto;width:88%">
    <div class="row">
    <% @winery.each do |t, a| %>
      
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h1 class="countrylabel <%= a['winery_id'] %>" style="font-family:oseb;"><%= a['name'] %></h1>
          <img src="<%= asset_path(a['image'])%>" class="country" style="height:400px">
        </div>
      
    <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>

